==================================================
4) GROQ OUTPUT CONTRACT (STRICT)
==================================================

Groq must return exactly:

{
  "approved": true,
  "confidence": 0.0,
  "market_state": "trend",
  "setup_quality": "A",
  "reason": "short technical reason",
  "entry_zone": {
    "min": 0.0,
    "max": 0.0
  },
  "stop_loss": 0.0,
  "take_profit": 0.0,
  "risk_note": "short note",
  "checkpoints": ["point1", "point2", "point3"]
}

Allowed values only:
- market_state:
  - trend
  - range
  - unclear

- setup_quality:
  - A
  - B
  - C
  - D

Not allowed:
- risk_reward
- position_sizing
- recommendations
- notes
- market_state แบบ uptrend/downtrend/bullish/weak
- setup_quality แบบ A-/B+/C-

==================================================
5) GROQ DECISION FLOW
==================================================

Python Candidate
  -> Groq Prompt Builder
  -> Groq Client Call
  -> Raw JSON Response
  -> Response Parser
  -> Output Validator
  -> Valid Decision
  -> ส่งต่อให้ Risk / Execution Layer

ถ้าพังที่ขั้นใดขั้นหนึ่ง:
  -> reject
  -> log error
  -> ไม่ส่งต่อ execution

==================================================
6) STATE DIAGRAM — GROQ LAYER
==================================================

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CandidateReady

    CandidateReady --> BuildPrompt
    BuildPrompt --> SendToGroq
    SendToGroq --> ReceiveResponse

    ReceiveResponse --> ParseJSON
    ParseJSON --> RejectInvalidJSON: parse failed
    ParseJSON --> ValidateSchema: parse passed

    ValidateSchema --> RejectSchemaError: missing key / extra key / wrong type
    ValidateSchema --> ValidateBusinessRules: schema passed

    ValidateBusinessRules --> RejectPolicyError: direction mismatch / invalid enum / invalid SL-TP
    ValidateBusinessRules --> DecisionAccepted: all checks passed

    RejectInvalidJSON --> LogReject
    RejectSchemaError --> LogReject
    RejectPolicyError --> LogReject

    DecisionAccepted --> ReturnValidatedDecision
    LogReject --> [*]
    ReturnValidatedDecision --> [*]

